The answer to Tom-Tell-Troth the practise of princes and the lamentations of the kirke / written by the Lord Baltismore, late secretary of state. Baltimore, George Calvert, Baron, 1580?-1632.
[2], 30 p.
[s.n.], London : 1642 [1643]
Dated by Thomason 25 February 1643. "Tom-Tell-Troth, or a free discourse", originally published about 1626 (STC 23868), was reprinted in 1642; Lord Baltimore's answer, written for Charles I early in his reign, had not previously been published. Reproduction of original in Thomason Collection, British Library.
